================================================================================
Third-party content (NOT covered by the MIT license above)
================================================================================

The MIT license covers the source code of this project. Some bundled data and
runtime assets are third-party content under their own terms:

- Korean dictionary data — `src/data/dictionary/ko.json`. Entries whose `source`
  field includes `krdict` are derived from the 국립국어원 한국어기초사전 (National
  Institute of Korean Language, Basic Korean Dictionary,
  https://krdict.korean.go.kr) and are licensed under Creative Commons
  Attribution-ShareAlike 2.0 Korea (CC BY-SA 2.0 KR,
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/kr/). They remain under that
  license: attribution to the institute is required, and adaptations must be
  distributed under the same license.

- Fonts — Fraunces, Newsreader, Spline Sans Mono, Noto Serif JP, and
  Noto Serif KR are loaded at runtime from the Google Fonts CDN and are NOT
  distributed with this repository. Each is licensed under the SIL Open Font
  License.

- 아리랑 (Arirang) — the lyrics and melody transcription in
  `src/data/koreanSongs.js` are a traditional Korean folk song in the public
  domain.
